The **~WatchPage** [[Help:WikiPlugin|plugin]] allows to manage notifications e-mails per page.

== Usage ==
{{{
<<WatchPage arguments>>
}}}

== Arguments ==

{| class="bordered"
|-
! Argument
! Description
! Default value
|-
| **page**
| The page to execute upon
| current pagename
|-
| **mode**
|
| add
|}

== Example ==

{{{
<<WatchPage page=HomePage>>
}}}

<<WatchPage page=HomePage>>

